title: Net Income of Farm Operators from Farming for United States
notes:
These Data Represent Gross Farm Income Minus Total Expenses Of Agricultural Production Plus A Correction For Inventory Differences. Data For 1940 And 1941 Are Preliminary. Source: U.S. Department Of Agriculture, Bureau Of Agricultural Economics, Agricultural Statistics, 1942, P. 662.

This NBER data series a08158 appears on the NBER website in Chapter 8 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter08.html.
